text: Mariyu ni prabhuvu: Tananu tappa itarulanu aradhincakudadani mariyu tallidandrulato mancitananto vyavaharincalani, ajnapinci unnadu. Okavela varilo e okkaru gani, leda variruvuru gani musalivaraite, varito visukkuntu: "Chi! (Uph)" ani kuda anaku mariyu varini gaddincaku mariyu varito maryadaga matladu
